French Lawmakers to Probe Areva’s UraMin, EDF, Tribune Reports

-- B y   T a r a   P a t e l
-- 
2011-06-28T05:40:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-28/french-lawmakers-to-probe-areva-s-uramin-edf-tribune-reports.html
French lawmakers plan to probe and
report on the finances of Areva SA and Electricite de France SA
focusing on the nuclear reactor builder’s acquisition of uranium
mining company UraMin,  La Tribune  reported, citing deputies.  Two lawmakers from the National Assembly’s finance
committee will also examine Areva’s ability to repay debt and
the financial situation of the EPR project in  Finland , the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tara Patel in Paris at 
 tpatel2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
